# 2. Find Index of an Element

## Problem

Find the position of a given element.

### Example

```python
numbers = (10, 20, 30, 40)
target = 30
```

## Built-in Solution

```python
numbers = (10, 20, 30, 40)

print(numbers.index(30))
```

## Pure Logic Solution

```python
numbers = (10, 20, 30, 40)
target = 30

for i in range(len(numbers)):

    if numbers[i] == target:
        print(i)
        break
```

### Output

